

Link-Parser
===========
To know about the Link-parser ,please see the web page http://www.abisource.com/projects/link-grammar/ 

And for Link-summary see the web page
http://www.abisource.com/projects/link-grammar/dict/index.html

Databases_used
==============

adverbs_list.gdbm  ---> This is a list of adverbs. We use it in identifying adverbs in Local word Grouping in a sentence.

           Ex: He has been frequently coming .

Here "frequently" is an adverb and it occurs in the group "has been frequently  coming".While grouping(lwg) we remove this adverb and group only "has been coming".

